{"tid":2414100,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"女子被控前年黃大仙參與非法集結 罪名不成立 同案其餘8被告早前已裁定表證不成立","createTime":"2021-02-19T07:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T10:14:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"78884bd01962c39bb7e945579f1e0dc63fdb239c","tid":2414100,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:22:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13781\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13781&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=f312d793\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13781</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#黃士翔裁判官 #裁決<br />\n#1001黃大仙 #非法集結 <br />\n<br />\n李（29） <br />\n<br />\n控罪： 非法集結<br />\n各被告同被控於於2019年10月1日在黃大仙鳳德道及盈鳳里，與其他不明人士參與 #非法集結 <br />\n<br />\n本案其餘8名被告較早前被黃士翔裁判官裁定表證不成立 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13494\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13494&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=2dba450a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13494</a>)<br />\n<br />\n審訊內容<br />\n<br />\nDay1AM (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13334\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13334&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=1f2c7a9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13334</a>) Day1PM (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13344\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13344&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=35593bc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13344</a>) (PW1 作供）<br />\nDay2AM (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13365\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13365&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=69122178\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13365</a>) (PW2作供）<br />\nDay2PM (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13398&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=c7854ea1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13398</a>) (PW3 作供）<br />\nDay3 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13401&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=8c8e1f69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13401</a>) (PW3 及PW4 作供）<br />\nDay4AM (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13423\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13423&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=9a5c72ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13423</a>) (PW5，PW6 及PW7作供)<br />\nDay4PM (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13435&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=8b5f85b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13435</a>) (PW8,PW9,PW10,PW11 及PW12作供）<br />\nDay5 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13452\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13452&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=3f711ceb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13452</a>) (控方及辯方作出中段陳詞）<br />\nDay6  (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13494\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13494&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=2dba450a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13494</a>)(法庭裁定D6表面證供成立)<br />\nDay7 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13532\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13532&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=5b0bb7dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13532</a>) (辯方結案陳詞 )<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n裁決速報：罪名不成立🥳💛"},{"pid":"2856a3dc98d6804fdc758433b85aa15f58387c52","tid":2414100,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:23:00.000Z","msg":"放過假先"},{"pid":"38bd3e6deb0b90a33c7740d312e917de1a903a6c","tid":2414100,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:26:13.000Z","msg":"如果係我 聽到嗰下真係會喊死<br />\n得自己一要繼續審落去<br />\n最後都可以同其他被告一齊冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e279553aa0bde65408a061216de420472cdc684","tid":2414100,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0bf50d235bb64ec402631e3eca43fba236ee8e","tid":2414100,"uid":126919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:32:01.000Z","msg":"希望831個手足都會一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"